Scrivener is also available for the iPad and iPhone (via the iOS App Store), so that you can work on your projects anywhere. Follow the instructions below to sync your Mac projects with our iOS version. Note that you will need a Dropbox account ({\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.getdropbox.com"}}{\fldrslt http://www.getdropbox.com}}) to sync. If you don\'92t have or want a Dropbox account, you can copy projects via iTunes (see below).\
