{\listtext	2.	}Select your device.\
{\listtext	3.	}Select \'93Apps\'94 in the sidebar.\
{\listtext	4.	}Scroll down to \'93File Sharing\'94.\
{\listtext	5.	}Select Scrivener in the \'93Apps\'94 list.\
{\listtext	6.	}Drag Scrivener projects from the Finder into the \'93Documents\'94 list in iTunes to copy projects to your device (or click on the \'93Add\'85\'94 button).\
{\listtext	7.	}Select a project in the \'93Documents\'94 list and click on \'93Save to\'85\'94 to copy a project from your device to your Mac\'92s hard drive.\
